snippet.title: Jurassic World Evolution 2 - First Look Species Field Guide - Future Games Show E3 2021
snippet.description:
In this short developer presentation for Jurassic World evolution 2 we hear about all the new features coming to the game as well as get a first look at gameplay with a short video focused on the Triceratops which is part of a wider Dinosaur focused series called Species Field Guide.
Jurassic World Evolution 2 is coming to  PS4, PS5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X and PC in 2021
